summary:
The Security Council,
Reaffirming all its previous resolutions on Western Sahara, in particular resolution 1429 (2002) of 30 July 2002,
Decides to extend the mandate of MINURSO until 31 March 2003 to consider the proposal presented by the Personal Envoy of the Secretary-General; 
Requests the Secretary-General to report on the situation by 17 March 2003; 
Decides to remain seized of the matter.
